Incarcinator's shells are HIGHLY explosive and VERY fast. If Scourge
got hit by two, it would probably do alot more damage than a simple
fleshwound.

::The Galactors/Incarcinator::

The Supernova/Slasys/Scrap jet makes an almost 90 degree turn upwards,
managing to avoid the shots. It turns, flying around for another pass.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Incarcinator fires two more shells before being hit by several blasts,
flipping backwards and trying to stabolize himself in the air.
